```r
age <- body_measurements$age
x2 <- seq(from = min(age), to = max(age), length = 100)
fun <- dnorm(x2, mean = mean(age), sd=sd(age))
hist(age,
     breaks = 25,
     main = "Distribution of age",
     xlab = "Age (years)",
     prob = TRUE,
     col = "gold")
lines(x = x2, 
      y = fun,
      col = "darkblue", 
      lwd=2)
lines(density(age), 
      col = "darkred", 
      lwd = 2)
